<p>Below are five legitimate, locally-operating septic companies serving the Des Moines metro in 2026. Each entry is based on the company's own website, third-party listings, and public records. No paid placements, no fluff.</p>

<h2>How We Ranked These Companies</h2>

<p>The list prioritizes companies that meet four criteria: a physical Des Moines metro presence, a clear focus on septic (not general plumbing with septic on the side), services covering both residential and commercial septic, and at least one decade in the local market. We did not rank by Google review count or BBB rating because both can be gamed and neither captures quality on a job site. Honest local reputation, transparent pricing, and Iowa Time of Transfer certification carry more weight here than star averages.</p>

